[src:flow-matching/optimal-transport] In this case, an optimal transport plan $\gamma \in \Gamma (\mu ,\nu )$ , constrains the form of an optimal pricing pair $(\varphi ,\psi )$ , and vice versa.
[src:flow-matching/optimal-transport] More succinctly, a transport plan is optimal iff it is supported on the set of *c*-subdifferential pairs of $(\varphi ,\psi )$ .
